SIALKOT,June 26 (APP)::Special Assistant to Prime Minister on Youth Affairs Usman Dar distributed face-masks among the general public and on Mujahid Road here after the Juma (Friday) prayers.
He stressed the need for social-distancing, self-isolation and wearing of face-masks to remain safe from coronavirus.
